================================================================================
Optional Runtime Components (if used in your services)
================================================================================

When building services on this template, track licenses for:
- Programming language runtimes (Node.js, PHP, Python, Go, etc.)
- Frameworks and libraries (Express, Laravel, React, etc.)
- Databases (MySQL/MariaDB, PostgreSQL, Redis, etc.)

For AMI/container distribution, generate a full dependency list using tools like:
- npm: `npx license-checker --summary`
- pip: `pip-licenses`
- Go: `go-licenses`
- General: FOSSA, Snyk, or Trivy

